atience%20As%20A%20Gift%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20the%20time%20I%20met%20this%20man%20I%20grew%20increasingly%20unsure%20of%E2%80%94he%20insisted%20on%20choosing%20the%20place%2C%20he%20ordered%20most%20of%20the%20food%2C%20but%20also%20indicated%20he'd%20like%20to%20pay%E2%80%94and%20after%20I%20said%20I%20wouldn't%20like%20to%20meet%20again%2C%20he%20insisted%20I%20pay%20him%20back%20(just%20don't%20offer%20to%20pay%20in%20the%20first%20place!%20Why%20make%20flimsy%20offers%20you%20won't%20stand%20by%20later%3F)%20Then%20there%20was%20another%20promising%20prospect%E2%80%94he%20was%20cute%2C%20and%20we'd%20been%20texting%20intensely%20for%20days%E2%80%94when%2C%20suddenly%2C%20just%20as%20we%20were%20deciding%20where%20to%20meet%2C%20he%20went%20silent.%20I%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20block%20him%E2%80%94that%20was%20better%20than%20sitting%20around%20and%20looking%20at%20my%20phone%20for%20hours%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20reply%20I%20was%20due%E2%80%94but%20it%20was%20still%20a%20tattered%20bandage%20over%20my%20yet%20again%20dashed%20hopes.%20There%20was%20another%20man%20who%20decided%2C%20a%20few%20silent%20weeks%20after%20some%20initial%20meetings%2C%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwasn't%20in%20a%20place%20to%20start%20something%20new%E2%80%9D.%20There%20was%20also%20the%20guy%20who%2C%20after%20a%20week%20of%20banter%2C%20chemistry%2C%20and%20regular%20talking%2C%20stopped%20replying%20when%20I%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20wanted%20in%20any%20relationship%2C%20in%20principle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20far%20from%20properly%20liking%20any%20of%20these%20people.%20But%20the%20hurt%20isn't%20so%20much%20heartache%20as%20it%20is%20from%20impatience%20and%20loss%20of%20faith.%20Each%20time%20the%20premise%20of%20the%20dating%20app%20is%20violated%E2%80%94that%20people%20will%20at%20least%20try%20to%20get%20to%20know%20each%20other%20sincerely%3B%20that%20the%20obstacle%20to%20a%20real%20relationship%20will%20be%20incompatibility%20or