ed%20love%3A%20by%20compressing%20people%20into%20six%20pictures%20and%20some%20boilerplate%20%E2%80%98witty'%20text%2C%20and%20making%20you%20think%20endlessly%20about%20these%20ideas%20of%20yourself%20and%20another%2C%20until%20the%20many-sided%20humanity%20of%20everyone%20involved%20becomes%20moot%3B%20by%20having%20a%20business%20model%20fundamentally%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20problem%20it's%20trying%20to%20solve%E2%80%94for%20every%20couple%20it%20creates%2C%20a%20dating%20app%20loses%20not%20one%20but%20two%20%E2%80%98users'%3B%20by%20dangling%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20new%20%E2%80%98perfect'%20connection%20at%20every%20turn%2C%20so%20if%20you%20find%20one%20thing%20you%20don't%20like%20about%20someone%2C%20you%20can%20just%20discard%20them%20and%20move%20on%20to%20the%20next.%20Soon%20our%20%E2%80%9CAI%20concierges%E2%80%9D%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20dating%20hundreds%20of%20other%20%E2%80%9CAI%20concierges%E2%80%9D%20on%20our%20behalf%2C%20to%20narrow%20us%20down%20to%20the%20evermore%20%E2%80%9Cperfect%E2%80%9D%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstagram%20seems%20to%20be%20reading%20between%20the%20lines%20of%20my%20WhatsApp%20chats%2C%20surfacing%20content%20that%20addresses%20these%20personal%20questions.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20someone%20can't%20meet%20your%20needs%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20why.%20Walk%20away%20and%20don't%20compromise%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20doesn't%20deserve%20you%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20right%20man%20will%20chase%20you%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CBe%20in%20your%20divine%20feminine.%20Cut%20people%20off%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20You%20Love%20Yourself%20A%20Little%20Too%20Much%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20help%20but%20feel%20tremendously%20confused%20about%20whether%20this%20emphasis%20on%20self-protection%2C%20disguised%20as%20self-care%2C%20is%20really%20in%20service%20to%20us%20not%20abandoning%20ourselves%20(which%20is%20advice%20I%20could%20really%20use%2C%20frankly)%E2%80%94or%20is%20it%20more%20of%20the%20hyper-individualism%20that%20we%20deem%20necessary%20to%20a%20healthy%20self-concept%20today%3F%20They%20say%20growth%20happens%20in%20the%20difficult%2C%20messy%20spaces%20of%20human%20connection%3B%20your%20ego%20may%20not%20feel%20like%20it's%20%E2%80%9Cwinning%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20you're%20being%20forced%20to%20change%20anyway.%20I%20wonder%20if%20the%20frequent%20conflation%20of%20compromise%20and%20%E2%80%98settling'%20with%20weakness%20or%20loss%20is%20creating%20a%20generation%20of%20emotionally%20stunted%E2%80%94endlessly%20seeking%20and%20isolated%E2%80%94people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20should%20we%20actually%20do%3F%20Well%2C%20if%20I%20knew%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20here%20trying%20to%20wring%20value%20from%20all%20my%20romantic%20failures%20in%20public.%20So%20now%20might%20be%20the%20time%20for%20you%20to%20stop%20reading%E2%80%94unless%20you're%20okay%20with%20less%20value%2C%20more%20entertainment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20answer%20in%20arranged%20marriages%20after%20all%2C%20which%20filters%20for%20seriousness%20of%20intent%20and%2C%20hopefully%2C%20integrity%3F%20I%20did%20make%20a%20Shaadi.com%20profile%20once%2C%20but%20the%20crowd%20there%20seemed%20so%20besmirched%20by%20people%20doing%20it%20for%20the%20wrong%20reasons%2C%20with%20an%20app%20interface%20that%20took%20me%20back%20to%201995%20and%20spam%20calls%20from%20suitors%20that%20put%20NoBroker%20to%20shame%2C%20that%20I%20didn't%20think%20anyone%20I'd%20love%20could%20be%20there.%20I%20uninstalled%20it%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20I%20simply%20give%20up%20on%20both%20the%20process%20and%20the%20outcome%2C%20and%20instead%20do%20things%20I%20love%20with%20the%20time%20recovered%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdating%20overhead%E2%80%9D%3F%20Perhaps%20I'll%20meet%20someone%20cool%20then.%20If%20not%2C%20I'll%20at%20least%20have%20spent%20my%20time%20the%20way%20I%20like%20to%2C%20and%20make%20more%20progress%20on%20things%20that%20are%20actually%20under%20my%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20those%20remaining%20exes%20in%20SF%E2%80%94do%20I%20actually%20come%20for%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Internal%20Journey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20real%20remedy%2C%20apart%20from%20making%20jokes%20about%20it%2C%20is%20internal%20and%20emotional.%20The%20%E2%80%98engineering'%20metaphor%20seems%20to%20last%3A%20the%20proportion%20of%20people%20who%20are%20happily%20married%20is%20probably%20comparable%20to%20those%20students%20who%20make%20it%20to%20the%20top%20colleges%3B%20yet%2C%20nearly%20everyone%20sits%20the%20exams%20with%20an%20equal%20amount%20of%20self-belief%2C%20at%20least%20in%20theory%2C%20hoping%20to%20make%20it.%20Only%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20being%20consumed%20by%20studies%20more%20than%20trying%20to%20meet%20people%20I'm%20not%20sure%20I'd%20like.%20But%20the%20odds%20of%20finding%20a%20partner%20are%20also%20better%20than%20succeeding%20in%20an%20education%20system%20designed%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20overall%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20resilience%20and%20detachment%20learnt%20in%20those%20teenage%20days%20would%20be%20the%20more%20necessary%20and%20valuable%20tenets%20to%20channel%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Framachandranesk%5C%22%3ESanjana%20Ramachandran%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Framachandranesk%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_campaign%3Dshare_via%26utm_content%3Dprofile%26utm_medium%3Dios_app%5C%22%3Ewriter%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20marketer%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%C2%A0with%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-linkindex%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20data-auth%3D%5C%22NotApplicable%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapc01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com%2F%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fx.com%252Framachandranesk%252Fstatus%252F1698942175034433863%26data%3D05