rnational%20Airport%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20visited%20Dubai%2027%20times%20in%20a%20year.%20The%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20officials%20have%20said%20the%2014.2%20kg%20haul%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20gold%20seizures%20at%20the%20Bengaluru%20airport%20in%20recent%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao%2C%20the%20stepdaughter%20of%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20Ramachandra%20Rao%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20Monday%20night%20by%20the%20officers%20of%20DRI.%20The%20agency%2C%20which%C2%A0operates%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%2C%20had%20been%20monitoring%20her%20movements%20due%20to%20her%20frequent%20trips%20to%20Dubai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Customs%20sought%20four-day%20custody%20of%20the%2033-year-old%20actor%20during%20the%20hearing%20of%20her%20bail%20petition.%C2%A0Objecting%20to%20this%2C%20her%20lawyer%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-ranya-rao-kannada-actor-arrested-on-gold-smuggling-charges-7851786%5C%22%3ERanya%20Rao%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody%20(from%20March%204%20to%20March%2018)%20as%20the%20DRI%20had%20no%20further%20questions%20for%20her.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20when%20she%20has%20moved%20a%20bail%20petition%2C%20the%20Custom%20department%20needs%20her%20custody%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%20The%20court%20has%20reserved%20the%20custody%20order%20for%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Lakhs%20In%20Commission%20For%20Smuggling%201%20Kg%20Gold'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%20has%20revealed%20that%20Ms%20Rao%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20gold%20smuggling%20network%20and%20took%20hefty%20commissions%20to%20smuggle%20goods%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20Indo-Asian%20News%20Service.%20The%20actor%20allegedly%20received%20around%20Rs%204%20lakh%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20in%20commission%20to%20smuggle%20one%20kilogram%20of%20gold%20from%20Dubai%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20seizure%20at%20the%20Bengaluru%20airport%2C%C2%A0searches%20were%20conducted%20at%20Ranya%20Rao's%20home%20and%20gold%20jewellery%20worth%20Rs%202.06%20crore%20and%20Indian%20currency%20amounting%20to%20Rs%202.67%20crore%20were%20also%20recovered%2C%20the%20DRI%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20interception%2C%20DRI%20officers%20searched%20her%20residence%20on%20Lavelle%20Road%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20she%20lives%20with%20her%20husband.%20The%20search%20led%20to%20the%20seizure%20of%20gold%20jewellery%20worth%20Rs%202.06%20crore%20and%20Indian%20currency%20amounting%20to%20Rs%202.67%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DRI%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BShocked%20And%20Devastated%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistancing%20himself%20from%20the%20case%2C%20the%20actor's%20stepfather%20said%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20Ms%20Rao%20and%20her%20husband's%20business%20dealings%20and%20that%20the%20law%20would%20take%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BLike%20any%20other%20father%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20and%20devastated%20when%20it%20came%20to%20my%20notice%20through%20the%20media.%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20of%20these%20things.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20anything%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Director-General%20of%20Police-rank%20officer%20also%20clarified%20that%20Ms%20Rao%20was%20not%20living%20with%20him.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20living%20separately%20with%20her%20husband.%20There%20must%20be%20some%20problem%20between%20them...%20(maybe)%20due%20to%20some%20family%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20is%20currently%20serving%20as%20the%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Police%20Housing%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'4%20