dia.%20People%20speaking%20different%20languages%20live%20in%20Mumbai%20as%20well.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20a%20natural%20expectation%20that%20they%20should%20also%20come%20here%20and%20learn%20Marathi%2C%20understand%20Marathi%20and%20read%20Marathi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20this%20is%20a%20great%20example%20of%20co-existence%20that%20people%20speaking%20so%20many%20different%20languages%20in%20India%20live%20together.%20I%20think%20that%20Mumbai%20is%20also%20an%20ideal%20example%20of%20this.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20natural%20expectation%20that%20a%20person%20coming%20to%20Mumbai%20should%20understand%20Marathi%2C%20speak%20Marathi%2C%20learn%20Marathi%2C%20read%20Marathi.%20This%20is%20the%20only%20expectation.%20I%20have%20nothing%20more%20to%20say%20than%20this...%20My%20mother%20tongue%20is%20Marathi.%20But%20I%20also%20respect%20the%20existence%20of%20all%20languages...%20I%20request%20everyone%20to%20see%20it%20from%20the%20same%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741258920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fo9jdlk38_fadnavis-joshi_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-suresh-bhaiyyaji-joshi-opposition-raises-marathi-row-over-rss-leaders-remarks-d-fadnavis-replies-7861693%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20uproar%20over%20senior%20RSS%20leader%20Suresh%20'Bhaiyyaji'%20Joshi's%20%26quot%3BMumbai%20has%20many%20languages%26quot%3B%20remark%2C%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20said%20the%20language%20of%20the%20state%20and%20Mumbai%20is%20Marathi%20and%20everyone%20should%20learn%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-suresh-bhaiyyaji-joshi-opposition-raises-marathi-row-over-rss-leaders-remarks-d-fadnavis-replies-7861693%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%