-hamas-before-issuing-threats-reports%2Famp_articleshow%2F118759971.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2226%2F11%20Accused%20Says%20Will%20Be%20Tortured%20In%20India%2C%20Wants%20Stay%20On%20Extradition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETahawwur%20Rana%2C%20accused%20in%20the%2026%2F11%20terror%20attacks%2C%20has%20asked%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20an%20emergency%20stay%20on%20his%20extradition%20to%20India%2C%20which%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20administration%20during%20the%20recent%20visit%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20In%20his%20petition%20--%20a%20last-ditch%20effort%20--%20Rana%20said%20he%20would%20be%20tortured%20and%20killed%20in%20India%20because%20of%20his%20national%2C%20religious%20and%20social%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20said%20he%20is%20a%20Muslim%20of%20Pakistani%20origin%20and%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%2C%20which%20would%20make%20him%20susceptible%20to%20torture%20in%20custody%20and%20that%20he%20could%20die%20given%20his%20health%20condition.%20Rana%20claimed%20he%20suffers%20from%20a%203.5%20cm%20abdominal%20aortic%20aneurysm%20that%20can%20rupture%20any%20time%2C%20Parkinson's%20disease%2C%20and%20possible%20bladder%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20petition%2C%20he%20said%20he%20cannot%20be%20sent%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bhornet's%20nest%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20is%20increasingly%20autocratic%2C%20citing%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%202023%20World%20Report%2C%20which%20alleges%20systematic%20discrimination%20and%20stigmatization%20of%20religious%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Muslims%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETahawwur%20Rana%20is%20a%20known%20associate%20of%20Pakistani-American%20terrorist%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20conspirators%20of%20the%20November%2026%2C%202008%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20in%20which%20166%20people%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHea