ebrates%20her%2028th%20birthday%20with%20heartfelt%20wishes%20from%20Bollywood%20stars%2C%20including%20Sidharth%20Malhotra%2C%20Varun%20Dhawan%2C%20and%20Ananya%20Panday.%20They%20shared%20unseen%20pictures%20and%20sweet%20messages.%20Collaborations%20with%20Sidharth%20in%20'Param%20Sundari'%20and%20Varun%20in%20'Sunny%20Sanskari%20Ki%20Tulsi%20Kumari'%20are%20highly%20anticipated.%20Janhvi%2C%20since%20her%20debut%20in%20'Dhadak'%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20promising%20talent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjanhvi-kapoor-turns-28-sidharth-malhotra-varun-dhawan-ananya-panday-shower-love-with-unseen-pics%2Farticleshow%2F118758798.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22While%20the%20US%20and%20China%20compete%20for%20AI%20dominance%2C%20Russia's%20leading%20model%20lags%20behind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20seated%20on%20stage%20at%20the%202022%20Russian%20AI%20Journey%20conference%2C%20against%20a%20bright%20blue%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b483567bb3f854015d1ba9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Vladimir%20Putin%20at%20the%202022%20Russian%20AI%20Journey%20conference.%3Cp%3EPavel%20Bednyakov%2C%20Sputnik%2C%20Kremlin%20Pool%20Photo%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussia%20has%20touted%20its%20leading%20LLM%2C%20GigaChat%20MAX%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20national%20AI%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20the%20model%20is%20%26quot%3Bunremarkable%26quot%3B%20and%20lags%20behind%20US%20and%20Chinese%20offerings%2C%20AI%20experts%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20stunted%20development%2C%20Moscow%20may%20still%20be%20developing%20military%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20wants%20his%20country%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20global%20race%20to%20build%20AI%2C%20besting%20models%20coming%20out%20of%20China%20and%20the%20US.%20But%20its%20flagship%20large%20language%20model%2C%20or%20LLM%2C%20isn't%20even%20the%20best%20at%20speaking%20Russian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fllmarena.ru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Russian-language%20version%20of%20LLM%20Arena%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20where%20users%20go%20to%20compare%20and%20rank%20the%20answers%20of%20different%20LLMs%20%E2%80%94%20GigaChat%20MAX%20comes%20joint-eighth%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20behind%20various%20versions%20of%20Claude%2C%20DeepSeek%2C%20and%20ChatGPT.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYandexGPT%204%20Pro%2C%20an%20LLM%20developed%20by%20the%20Russian%20search%20engine%20Yandex%2C%20is%20even%20lower%2C%20at%20joint%2018th.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20English-language%20version%2C%20neither%20appears%20in%20the%20ranking%20of%20more%20than%20170%20LLMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGigaChat%20MAX%20was%20developed%20by%20Russia's%20state-majority-owned%20Sberbank.%20When%20its%20latest%20iteration%20launched%20in%20November%2C%20its%20Moscow-based%20lead%20developer%2C%20Evgeny%20Kosarev%2C%20said%20on%20LinkedIn%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bclose%20to%20GPT4o%20in%20quality%20on%20Russian%20and%20English.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20experts%20have%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%2C%20despite%20Putin%20emphasizing%20AI%20development%20as%20a%20crucial%20avenue%20for%20Russian%20foreign%20policy%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGigaChat%20MAX%20is%20months%20behind%20American%20and%20Chinese%20competitors.%20The%20country's%20war%20against%20Ukraine%20has%20also%20drained%20it%20of%20expertise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20GigaChat%20MAX%20and%20Yandex%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8f7d19d-4865-43b6-9c43-ffd6563ab0b6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20'unremarkable'%20model%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGigaChat%20MAX%2C%20Russia's%20most%20developed%20LLM%2C%20is%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bunremarkable%2C%26quot%3B%20Lukasz%20Olejnik%2C%20a%20visiting%20senior%20research%20fellow%20in%20cybersecurity%20at%20the%20War%20Studies%20department%20at%20King's%20College%2C%20London%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%26quot%3Bbenchmarks%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20standardized%20tests%20for%20AI%20effectiveness%20%E2%80%94%20the%20models'%20scores%20%26quot%3Bare%20much%20lower%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20don't%20surpass%20any%20of%20the%20cutting-edge%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bfrontier%2C%26quot%3B%20models%2C%20and%20don't%20involve%20any%20particular%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Dubow%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20European%20Policy%20Analysis%20and%20CTO%20of%20data-analysis%20firm%20Omelas%2C%20added%20that%20GigaChat%20MAX%20lacked%20an%20edge%20in%20many%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20handles%20math%20well%2C%20in%20the%20Russian%20language%20it%20is%20far%20behind%20most%20leading%20Western%20and%20Chinese%20LLMs%20on%20some%20benchmarks%2C%20Dubow%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themoscowtimes.com%2F2025%2F01%2F28%2Frussian-ai-struggles-in-its-own-language-a87773%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20The%20Moscow%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20leading%20LLMs%20developed%20in%20the%20US%20were%20a%20year%20ahead%20of%20GigaChat%20MAX's%20current%20level%20on%20the%20industry-standard%20%26quot%3BMassive%20Multitask%20Language%20Understanding%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20MMLU%2C%20which%20tests%20an%20LLM's%20general%20knowledge%20and%20problem-solving%20ability%20in%20text-based%20answers%20across%20a%20huge%20range%20of%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDubow%20also%20told%20BI%20that%20most%20AIs%20are%20being%20held%20to%20more%20advanced%20benchmarks%2C%20with%20MMLU%20%26quot%3Balmost%20considered%20pass%C3%A9%20at%20this%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBesting%20American%20and%20Chinese%20models%20on%20Russian%20language%20prompts%20is%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20the%20Russian%20government's%20AI%20strategy%2C%20but%20MAX%20has%20not%20achieved%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Dubow%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220588cc06-7b78-4a05-8361-69e59837fad4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20holding%20Russia's%20AI%20development%20back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20repeatedly%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20AI%2C%20including%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fen.kremlin.ru%2Fevents%2Fpresident%2Fnews%2F75830%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20December%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20he%20touted%20GigaChat%20MAX%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fen.kremlin.ru%2Fevents%2Fpresident%2Fnews%2F75830%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Russia%20was%20ready%20to%20assist%20other%20nations%20with%20developing%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamuel%20Bendett%2C%20a%20specialist%20in%20Russian%20military%20technology%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etold%20BI%20that%20AI%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20status%20thing%26quot%3B%20for%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tortoisemedia.com%2Fintelligence%2Fglobal-ai%23rankings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20global%20AI%20ranking%3C%2Fa%3E%20produced%20by%20UK%20media%20startup%20Tortoise%20Media%2C%20Russia%20is%20the%20only%20one%20out%20of%20the%20five%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20power%26quot%3B%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20the%20US%2C%20China%2C%20France%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20Russia%20%E2%80%94%20not%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list.%20Russia%20is%20ranked%2031st.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBendett%20named%20several%20factors%20holding%20Moscow's%20AI%20sector%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20private%20sector%20is%20too%20small%20to%20foster%20real%20competition%2C%20with%20almost%20everything%20government-supported%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sberbank%20CEO%20German%20Gref%2C%20seated%2C%20looks%20on%20as%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20addresses%20the%202022%20AI%20Journey%20conference%20on%20a%20stage%20highlighted%20in%20neon%20green.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b484607bb3f854015d1bc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESberbank%20CEO%20German%20Gref%20listens%20to%20Putin%20at%20the%202022%20AI%20Journey%20conference.%3Cp%3EPavel%20Bednyakov%2C%20Sputnik%2C%20Kremlin%20Pool%20Photo%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Sberbank%20is%20increasingly%20casting%20itself%20as%20a%20technology%20company%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20equivalent%20to%20OpenAI%20and%20Microsoft%20or%20Google%20or%20Huawei%20or%20Alibaba%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20has%20isolated%20it%20from%20both%20global%20expertise%20and%20collaboration%2C%20as%20well%20as%20access%20to%20tech%20like%20microchips%20necessary%20to%20train%20and%20run%20complex%20AI%20models%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20story%20of%20the%20Russian%20AI%20industry%20is%2C%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20Putin's%20expansionism%20undermining%20Russia's%20global%20standing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dubow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2014%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Russia%20annexed%20Crimea%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20transformative%20year%20for%20AI%20in%20the%20West%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%202022%2C%20the%20year%20Russia%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20was%20the%20year%20ChatGPT%20launched%2C%20sparking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-changed-everything-and-was-a-black-swan-event-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20generative%20AI%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewar%20in%20Ukraine%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eaccelerated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-outlook-ukraine-war-worker-shortage-population-brain-drain-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20major%20brain%20drain%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Russia%2C%20according%20to%20Dubow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBendett%20added%20that%20Russia%20lacks%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20thousands%26quot%3B%20of%20high-tech%20researchers%2C%20although%20he%20said%20that%20he%20believed%20many%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Btech%20refugees%26quot%3B%20who%20left%20Russia%20to%20avoid%20the%20draft%20have%20started%20to%20trickle%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Feconomy%2F1747201%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacknowledged%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20problems%20last%20year%2C%20blaming%20%26quot%3Bunfriendly%20countries%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20roadblocks%20and%20vowing%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20people%20graduating%20in%20AI%20technology%20to%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20a%20year%20by%202030%2C%20Russia's%20TASS%20news%20agency%20reported%2C%20citing%20government%20documents.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20just%203%2C000%20graduated%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20the%20US%20had%20more%20than%2073%2C000%20graduates%20in%20AI-related%20fields%20in%202023%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20whom%20were%20international%20talent%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcset.georgetown.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FKeeping-Top-AI-Talent-in-the-United-States.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Center%20for%20Security%20and%20Emerging%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerhii