hes-delhi-mumbai-pet-friendly-rides-huft-partnership-125030600670_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brevan%20Howard's%20pitch%20to%20deep-pocketed%20investors%3A%20The%20'true%20risk'%20of%20crypto%20is%20not%20having%20exposure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aron%20Landy%2C%20Brevan%20Howard%20CEO%2C%20posing%20with%20his%20arms%20crossed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c89eecb8b41a9673f9c4fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrevan%20Howard%20CEO%20Aron%20Landy.%3Cp%3EBrevan%20Howard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBrevan%20Howard%20believes%20institutions%20are%20close%20to%20diving%20into%20crypto%20after%20years%20of%20weariness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20firm's%20digital%20assets%20unit%20was%20up%20more%20than%2052%25%20in%202024%20and%20employs%20more%20than%2060%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrevan%20Howard%20Digital%20aims%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20leading%20asset%20manager%20for%20institutional%20investors%26quot%3B%20in%20crypto.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAron%20Landy%20%E2%80%94%20the%20CEO%20of%20%2434%20billion%20macro%20investment%20manager%20Brevan%20Howard%20%E2%80%94%20believes%20the%20%26quot%3Btipping%20point%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20lead%20institutional%20investors%20to%20pile%20into%20crypto%20is%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20of%20volatility%20and%20big-name%20bad%20actors%20have%20kept%20institutions%20away%20from%20digital%20assets.%20Still%2C%20with%20a%20new%20administration%20in%20the%20US%20and%20asset%20managers%20like%20BlackRock%20and%20Fidelity%20becoming%20more%20entrenched%20in%20the%20space%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20investors%20will%20slowly%20wade%20into%20the%20space%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20dive%20fully%20in.%20London-based%20Brevan%20Howard%2C%20through%20its%20%242.5%20billion%20stand-alone%20crypto%20unit%20that%20was%20up%20over%2052%25%20last%20year%2C%20is%20aiming%20to%20be%20the%20place%20to%20go%20for%20crypto-curious%20institutions.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20predominant%20mindset%20in%20the%20institutional%20space%20has%20been%20that%20any%20exposure%20to%20digital%20assets%20is%20a%20little%20too%20volatile%2C%26quot%3B%20Landy%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20a%20shift%20in%20mindset%20is%20happening%20and%20that%20soon%2C%20even%20this%20year%2C%20having%20zero%20exposure%20to%20digital%20assets%20will%20be%20the%20true%20risk.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20moment%2C%20it's%20kind%20of%20a%20separate%20asset%20class%2C%20but%20over%20time%2C%20there'll%20be%20a%20convergence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20convergence%20may%20be%20sped%20up%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration.%20After%20years%20of%20frustration%20under%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20SEC%20commissioner%20Gary%20Gensler%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20and%20his%20crypto%20czar%20David%20Sacks%20have%20provided%20a%20jolt%20to%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20have%20been%20frustrated%20with%20the%20administration's%20crypto%20agenda%2C%20including%20the%20creation%20of%20meme%20coins%20related%20to%20Trump%20and%20the%20first%20lady%2C%20Melania%20Trump%2C%20and%20the%20strategic%20reserve%20of%20different%20digital%20assets%2C%20the%20election%20was%20a%20positive%20change%20for%20the%20industry%2C%20said%20Gautam%20Sharma%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20Brevan%20Howard%20Digital.%20Sharma%20declined%20to%20provide%20additional%20comment%20on%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20size%20of%20the%20talent%20pool%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20capital%20in%20the%20US%20means%20the%20%26quot%3Bvibe%26quot%3B%20around%20an%20industry%20can%20matter%20just%20as%20much%20as%20a%20specific%20policy%2C%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrevan%20thinks%20of%20the%20industry%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btransformational%20technology%26quot%3B%20akin%20to%20the%20internet%2C%20Landy%20said%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bany%20new%20innovation%20needs%20two%20things%3A%20talent%20and%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%20The%20two%20executives%20said%20there%20should%20be%20plenty%20of%20momentum%20to%20attract%20ambitious%20young%20people%20to%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20digital%20asset%20universe%20has%20tailwinds%2C%20not%20headwinds%2C%26quot%3B%20Landy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a3f827f-d9b4-436a-b543-9781fa01ae72%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInside%20Brevan%20Howard%20Digital%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESeptember%20will%20be%20the%20unit's%20fourth%20anniversary%2C%20and%20Sharma%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20goal%20remains%20the%20same%20as%20when%20they%20launched%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20objective%20is%20to%20be%20the%20leading%20asset%20manager%20for%20institutional%20investors%20in%20digital%20assets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20manager%20is%20working%20on%20a%20few%20additional%20products%20for%20institutional%20investors%20to%20add%20alongside%20its%20flagship%20multi-manager%20crypto%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20digital%20asset%20space%20becomes%20more%20integrated%20into%20financial%20institutions%20and%20accepted%20by%20regulators%2C%20big-name%20asset%20managers%20will%20follow%20suit.%20Former%20crypto%20critics%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fken-griffin-crypto-jihadist-call-against-dollar-regulation-citadel-securities-2021-10%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20Citadel%20Securities'%20Ken%20Griffin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20embracing%20the%20space%20and%20building%20out%20their%20offerings%20because%20of%20the%20tailwinds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20alternative%20investors%2C%20especially%20those%20catering%20to%20large%20institutional%20investors%20like%20sovereign%20wealth%20and%20pension%20funds%2C%20Brevan%20has%20a%20relative%20headstart%20thanks%20partly%20to%20its%20founder%2C%20billionaire%20Alan%20Howard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoward%20has%20been%20interested%20in%20the%20space%20for%20close%20to%20a%20decade%20and%20started%20investing%20his%20personal%20capital%20in%202016%20and%20has%20seen%20firsthand%20how%20the%20industry%20has%20changed%2C%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlan%20understands%20this%20space%20better%20than%20most%2C%20not%20just%20the%20investing%20side%20of%20it%20but%20the%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sharma%2C%20who%20previously%20ran%20internal%20projects%20for%20the%20hedge%20fund%20and%20oversaw%20the%20buildout%20of%20the%20digital%20assets%20business%20alongside%20Natalie%20Smith%2C%20the%20firm's%20head%20of%20strategy%20and%20client%20partnership%20group.%20Howard's%20enthusiasm%20led%20Brevan%20Howard%20Digital%20to%20focus%20not%20just%20on%20hiring%20investing%20staff%2C%20technologists%2C%20and%20engineers.%20The%20firm%20built%20the%20unit's%20infrastructure%20from%20scratch%20over%20six%20months%20in%202021%20and%20now%20has%20a%20team%20of%20more%20than%2060%20people%20in%20eight%20offices%20that%20can%20trade%20around%20the%20clock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d91c4bb-5122-4b14-8bc6-32d8183b3006%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThinking%20long-term%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20close%20to%20Brevan%20said%20the%20firm's%20digital%20asset%20investment%20products%20have%20%26quot%3Brelatively%20long%20lock-up%20periods%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20the%20firm%20withstand%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20aligns%20with%20the%20firm's%20belief%20that%20small%20bumps%20in%20the%20road%20will%20be%20just%20that%3A%20bumps%20in%20the%20road.%20The%20digital%20asset%20industry%20%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20worth%20many%20multiples%20than%20what%20it%20is%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Landy%20said%2C%20and%20the%20firm%20wants%20to%20partner%20with%20institutions%20willing%20to%20back%20that%20long-term%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20separate%20digital-asset%20unit%20invests%20in%20liquid%20coins%20such%20as%20Bitcoin%20but%20also%20options%2C%20derivatives%2C%20and%20private%20stakes%20in%20startups.%20Brevan%20Howard%20Digital%20also%20helps%20diversity%20the%20firm's%20largest%20multistrategy%20funds%2C%20managing%20sleeves%20of%20capital%20for%20the%20%2412%20billion%20master%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20to%20invest%20is%20not%20because%20it's%20going%20up%2C%20or%20that%20it's%20gone%20down%20and%20therefore%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20instead%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20something%20transformational%20for%20all%20industries%2C%20Landy%20said.%20The%20firm's%20conviction%20in%20the%20industry%20comes%20not%20just%20from%20Howard's%20personal%20interest%2C%20but%20the%20many%20engineers%20and%20technologists%20inside%20the%20firm%20who%20have%20been%20passionate%20about%20the%20space%20for%20years%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20macro%20investing%20perspective%2C%20investors%20should%20have%20some%20exposure%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20the%20firm%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Btipping%20point%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20institutions%20flooding%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20some%20exposure%20will%20be%20the%20norm%2C%26quot%3B%20Landy%20said%2C%20and%20those%20who%20choose%20Brevan%20%26quot%3Binvest%20with%20us%20because%20they%20want%20our%20expertise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrevan-howard-digital-assets-crypto-investing-investor-pitch-aron-landy-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741255381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c89f0b69253ccddf985e77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreva