%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c8b76569253ccddf9863f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20audiences%20could%20stream%20this%20week's%20Oscars%20on%20Hulu.%20That%20helped%20the%20show%2C%20which%20featured%20a%20performance%20by%20Cynthia%20Erivo%20and%20Ariana%20Grande%2C%20deliver%20its%20biggest%20audience%20in%20five%20years.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Winter%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETV%20audiences%20have%20been%20shrinking%20for%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20if%20you%20stream%20big%2C%20live%20TV%20shows%20on%20services%20people%20use%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-much-is-hulu%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHulu%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20people%20will%20watch%20them%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20helped%20boost%20the%20ratings%20for%20this%20week's%20Oscars%2C%20last%20month's%20Super%20Bowl%2C%20and%20last%20year's%20Olympics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERadical%20idea%3A%20What%20if%20TV%20networks%2C%20which%20are%20struggling%20to%20keep%20their%20audiences%2C%20streamed%20their%20biggest%2C%20most%20popular%20programs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%2C%20I%20know%3A%20It's%20not%20a%20radical%20idea.%20And%20the%20TV%20guys%20have%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20years%2C%20and%20it%20hasn't%20been%20helping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcept%20it%20seems%20like%20it%20%3Cem%3Ehas%3C%2Fem%3E%20been%20helping.%20Turns%20out%20that%20if%20you%20let%20people%20stream%20the%20biggest%20shows%20on%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20live%2C%20must-see%20sports%20and%20live%2C%20must-see%20awards%20shows%20%E2%80%94%20more%20people%20%3Cem%3Ewill%3C%2Fem%3E%20watch%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20new%20confirmation%20of%20that%20this%20week%20when%20Disney%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20goosed%20ratings%20for%20this%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foscar-nominations-academy-award-nominees-winners-list-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOscars%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20streaming%20them%20on%20its%20Hulu%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Disney%20hasn't%20provided%20a%20full%20breakout%20of%20its%20audience%20on%20Hulu%20compared%20to%20conventional%20TV%2C%20it%20said%20viewing%20on%20phones%20and%20other%20devices%20%E2%80%94%20the%20majority%20of%20which%20presumably%20came%20from%20Hulu%20users%20%E2%80%94%20boosted%20ratings%20by%201.65%20million%20viewers%2C%20for%20a%20total%20of%2019.7%20million%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20tiny%20increase%20of%20200%2C000%20viewers%20over%20last%20year's%20show.%20But%20in%20an%20era%20of%20shrinking%20ratings%2C%20that%20was%20enough%20to%20make%20it%20the%20most%20popular%20Oscars%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Fox%2C%20which%20streamed%20last%20month's%20Super%20Bowl%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftubi-fox-streamer-black-viewers-super-bowl-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETubi%3C%2Fa%3E%20service%2C%20says%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.tubitv.com%2Fpress%2F4545%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E13.6%20million%20people%20watched%20the%20game%20that%20way%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20helped%20make%20it%20the%20most-watched%20Super%20Bowl%20in%20history%2C%20with%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nielsen.com%2Fnews-center%2F2025%2Fsuper-bowl-lix-makes-tv-history-with-over-127-million-viewers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E128%20million%20viewers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20last%20year%2C%20Comcast%20said%20that%20about%2013.5%25%20of%20its%20summer%20Olympics%20audience%20came%20from%20streaming%2C%20with%20its%20Peacock%20service%20accounting%20for%20most%20of%20that.%20That%20helped%20create%20a%20huge%20increase%20over%20the%20previous%20summer%20Olympics%20(the%20fact%20that%20last%20year's%20games%20were%20in%20Paris%2C%20which%20made%20it%20much%20easier%20for%20US%20audiences%20to%20watch%20live%20than%20the%20previous%20games%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20is%20also%20meaningful).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20that's%20three%20examples%2C%20and%20Journalism%20Law%20means%20that's%20officially%20a%20Trend.%20But%20it's%20also%20completely%20obvious.%20How%20come%20the%20TV%20guys%20weren't%20doing%20this%20before%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20that%20one%20is%20a%20little%20complicated.%20One%20answer%20is%20that%20in%20some%20cases%20they%20%3Cem%3Ehave%3C%2Fem%3E%20been%20streaming%20this%20stuff%20before.%20It's%20been%20possible%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2F2016%2F2%2F8%2F11587672%2Fmore-people-streamed-the-super-bowl-than-ever-before%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estream%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20(legally)%20for%20many%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20via%20a%20broadcaster's%20site%20or%20dedicated%20app.%20And%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20it's%20been%20held%20up%20by%20contract%20clauses%20meant%20to%20protect%20broadcasters'%20local%20TV%20stations%2C%20who%20didn't%20want%20to%20lose%20eyeballs%20to%20streaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20truly%20big%20change%20that's%20happened%20isn't%20just%20that%20the%20TV%20guys%20are%20streaming%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20%3Cem%3Ehow%3C%2Fem%3E%20they're%20streaming.%20By%20putting%20the%20events%20on%20big%2C%20well-distributed%20apps%2C%20the%20TV%20guys%20are%20finding%20audiences%20where%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20could%20only%20stream%20the%20Oscars%20via%20an%20ABC%20site%2C%20or%20the%20Super%20Bowl%20through%20a%20Fox%20site%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20you'd%20see%20a%20serious%20audience%20boost%2C%20because%20cord-cutting%2Fcord-nevering%20audiences%20would%20be%20unlikely%20to%20find%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Hulu%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%2054%20million%20subscribers.%20Tubi%20has%20around%20100%20million%20users.%20Turns%20out%20that%20putting%20big%2C%20live%20events%20on%20them%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20events%20that%20still%20draw%20big%20audiences%20on%20regular%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20will%20work%20there%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foscars-super-bowl-streaming-tv-networks-disney-hulu-fox-tubi-2025-03%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741255261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c8b77469253ccddf9863fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foscars-super-bowl-streaming-tv-networks-disney-hulu-fox-tubi-2025-03%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TV%20audiences%20have%20been%20shrinking%20for%20years.%20But%20if%20you%20stream%20big%2C%20live%20TV%20shows%20on%20services%20people%20use%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Hulu%20%E2%80%94%20people%20will%20watch%20them%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foscars-super-bowl-streaming-tv-networks-disney-hulu-fox-tubi-2025-03%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Artist%20abandons%20plan%20to%20starve%20piglets%20to%20death%20after%20animals%20stolen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741255260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F03%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-piglets-denmark_6847835.jpg%3F20250306102719%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fartist-abandons-plan-to-starve-piglets-to-death-after-animals-stolen-13322612%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20artist%20who%20tried%20to%20starve%20three%20piglets%20to%20death%20as%20part%20of%20a%20controversial%20exhibition%20says%20he%20has%20changed%20his%20plan%20after%20the%20animals%20were%20stolen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.