k%20Partners%20surveyed%20more%20than%20900%20investment%20bankers%20about%20their%202024%20salaries%20and%20bonuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20was%20conducted%20between%20December%201%2C%202024%20and%20February%2028%2C%202025%20using%20Prospect%20Rock's%20banking%20industry%20contacts.%20It's%20the%20third%20year%20Meridith%20Dennes%2C%20the%20firm's%20managing%20partner%2C%20has%20conducted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20been%20so%20cryptic%2C%26quot%3B%20Dennes%20told%20Business%20Insider%20about%20the%20Wall%20Street%20compensation%20structure.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20point%20of%20the%20survey%20is%20that%20compensation%20is%20much%20more%20nuanced%20than%20what%20people%20talk%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurvey%20respondents%20included%20bankers%20from%20all%20ranks%2C%20from%20analysts%20up%20to%20vice%20presidents%20and%20managing%20directors%2C%20and%20across%20a%20multitude%20of%20coverage%20groups%2C%20and%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProspect%20Rock%20Partners%20gave%20BI%20permission%20to%20publish%20select%20slides%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprospectrockpartners.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20full%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20results%20shared%20here%20suggest%20that%20so-called%20elite%20boutique%20banks%20(think%20Evercore%2C%20Lazard%2C%20and%20Centerview)%20saw%20total%20compensation%20increases%20of%20between%2011%25%20to%2068%25%20across%20all%20roles.%20Total%20pay%20for%20associates%20at%20elite%20boutiques%20rose%20an%20average%20of%2031%25%20for%20first-year%20associates%20and%2033%25%20for%20second-year%20associates.%20Managing%20director%20compensation%20at%20elite%20boutiques%20jumped%20from%20about%20%241%20million%20in%202023%20to%20over%20%241.7%20million%20in%202024%2C%20an%20increase%20of%2068%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20bonus%20insights%20come%20as%20Wall%20Street%20waits%20with%20bated%20breath%20to%20see%20whether%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid