articles%2Fcr52vyepp8lo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20A%20PhD%20Student%20Became%20One%20Of%20UK's%20Most%20Dangerous%20Sexual%20Predators%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20PhD%20student%2C%20convicted%20of%20drugging%20and%20assaulting%20multiple%20women%2C%20could%20be%20among%20the%20most%20prolific%20sexual%20predators%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20investigators%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhenhao%20Zou%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20Chinese%20national%2C%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20multiple%20charges%2C%20including%20rape%2C%20voyeurism%20and%20possession%20of%20pornographic%20material.%20Law%20enforcement%20officials%20fear%20the%20number%20of%20his%20victims%20may%20be%20much%20higher%20than%20currently%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Zhenhao%20Zou%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20China%2C%20Zou%20came%20to%20the%20UK%20in%202017%20to%20pursue%20higher%20education.%20He%20was%20studying%20at%20Queen's%20University%20in%20Belfast%20before%20moving%20to%20London%20in%202019%20for%20a%20master's%20degree%2C%20and%20later%20a%20PhD%20at%20University%20College%20London%20(UCL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20wealthy%20background%2C%20he%20led%20a%20life%20of%20luxury.%20He%20used%20to%20spend%20thousands%20on%20rent%2C%20designer%20clothing%20and%20cosmetic%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20he%20did%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZou%20planned%20his%20assaults%2C%20using%20hidden%20cameras%20to%20record%20his%20victims%20without%20their%20knowledge.%20His%20crimes%20spanned%20both%20the%20UK%20and%20China.%20The%20attacks%20reportedly%20occurred%20between%202019%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20found%20that%20he%20used%20drugs%2C%20including%20ecstasy%20and%20an%20industrial%20chemical%20that%20converts%20into%20GHB%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdate-rape%26quot%3B%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20found%20a%20collection%20of%20his%20victims'%20clothing%20and%20jewellery%20from%20him.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcwyjxv1j9g8o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Zou%20recorded%20nine%20assaults%20as%20%26quot%3Bsouvenirs%26quot%3B%20and%20kept%20a%20trophy%20box%20containing%20his%20victims'%20jewellery%20and%20clothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvidence%20against%20him%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20presented%20extensive%20video%20footage%20of%20the%20assaults%2C%20revealing%20horrifying%20details%20of%20how%20Zou%20preyed%20on%20unconscious%20or%20semi-conscious%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20jurors%20had%20to%20watch%20disturbing%20footage%20of%20nine%20rapes%2C%20leading%20to%20visibly%20emotional%20reactions%20in%20the%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Rosina%20Cottage%20described%20Zou%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20and%20predatory%26quot%3B%20offender%20and%20warned%20that%20he%20faces%20a%20lengthy%20prison%20sentence%2C%20set%20to%20be%20delivered%20on%20June%2019%2C%20stated%20the%20BBC%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScale%20of%20the%20crimes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetectives%20from%20the%20Metropolitan%20Police%20believe%20there%20could%20be%20as%20many%20as%2050%20more%20victims.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20is%20the%20insidious%20nature%20of%20these%20offences%2C%20I%20think%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20many%20more%20victim-survivors%20may%20not%20even%20know%20that%20he%20has%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20raped%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Cdr%20Kevin%20Southworth%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20media%20coverage%20of%20the%20case%2C%20at%20least%20one%20woman%20has%20contacted%20the%20police%20with%20concerns%20about%20Zou.%20Authorities%20are%20now%20urging%20more%20victims%2C%20particularly%20from%20the%20Chinese%20student%20community%20in%20London%2C%20to%20come%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20woman%20who's%20in%20any%20way%20had%20a%20one-on-one%20encounter%20with%20this%20man%20Zou%2C%20then%20we%20would%20like%20to%20hear%20from%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Cdr%20Southworth%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20proceedings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZou%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%2011%20counts%20of%20rape%2C%20with%20two%20offences%20involving%20the%20same%20victim.%20He%20was%20also%20convicted%20of%20three%20counts%20of%20voyeurism%2C%2010%20counts%20of%20possessing%20extreme%20pornographic%20images%20and%20one%20count%20of%20false%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20also%20found%20him%20guilty%20of%20three%20counts%20of%20possessing%20a%20controlled%20drug%20with%20intent%20to%20commit%20a%20sexual%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20defence%2C%20Zou%20claimed%20that%20his%20actions%20were%20consensual%20and%20part%20of%20a%20pre-discussed%20role-play%20scenario%20with%20one%20of%20the%20women%20he%20filmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUniversity%20and%20prosecutors%20respond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUCL%20president%20Dr%20Michael%20Spence%20said%20that%20they%20were%20appalled%20by%20these%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaira%20Pike%20from%20the%20Crown%20Prosecution%20Service%20thanked%20the%20women%20who%20came%20forward%20to%20report%20Zou's%20crimes%2C%20stating%20that%20they%20have%20been%20incredibly%20strong%20and%20brave%20%26quot%3BZou%20is%20a%20serial%20rapist%20and%20a%20danger%20to%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Pike.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741252560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Facjq0gfg_zhenhao-zou_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-zhenhao-zou-one-of-the-most-prolific-sexual-predators-in-uk-7860586%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20PhD%20student%2C%20convicted%20of%20drugging%20and%20assaulting%20multiple%20women%2C%20could%20be%2