d%20who%20am%20I%20to%20impose%20my%20opinion%20on%20him%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Aiyar%20said%20he%20hopes%20that%20some%20people%20go%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi%20to%20complain%20about%20him%20and%20that%20makes%20him%20take%20note%20of%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20he%20does%20not%20meet%20Mr%20Gandhi%20personally%20and%20clear%20the%20misunderstandings%2C%20Mr%20Aiyar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20will%20I%20meet%20him%20if%20he%20doesn't%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20narrated%20an%20anecdote%20about%20a%20conversation%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20back%20in%202004.%20Mr%20Aiyar%20said%20that%20during%20a%20discussion%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20security%20cover%2C%20his%20wife%20Suneet%20Mani%20Aiyar%20had%20told%20Rahul%20not%20to%20listen%20to%20him.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Rahul)%20replied%2C%20'I%20would%20always%20listen%20to%20him%20because%20he%20is%20my%20father's%20friend%20and%20my%20father%20always%20listened%20to%20him.'%20And%20now%20he%20does%20not%20meet%20me.%20Neither%20him%20nor%20Priyanka%20(Gandhi%20Vadra).%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20(health)%20condition%20is%20not%20good.%20But%20I%20cannot%20meet%20anyone.%20And%20why%20should%20I%20disturb%20them%3F%20Should%20I%20go%20and%20ask%20for%20an%20MP%20post%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clip%20of%20Mr%20Aiyar's%20remarks%20on%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20academic%20setbacks%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyar-rajiv-gandhi-rajiv-failed-at-cambridge-mani-shankar-aiyar-redux-bjp-makes-most-of-it-7860060%5C%22%3Esparked%20a%20row%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20using%20it%20to%20target%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20responding%20by%20dismissing%20the%20veteran%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20short%20clip%20from%20the%20nearly%20two-and-a-half-hour%20interview%20that%20is%20doing%20the%20rounds%20shows%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20pilot.%20He%20has%20failed%20twice.%20I%20was%20with%20him%20at%20Cambridge.%20He%20failed%20there.%20And%20failing%20in%20Cambridge%20is%20very%20difficult.%20It%20is%20easy%20to%20get%20a%20first-class.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20university%20wants%20to%20maintain%20its%20image%20and%20tries%20to%20ensure%20everyone%20at%20least%20passes.%20Then%20he%20went%20to%20Imperial%20College%2C%20London%2C%20and%20failed%20again.%20So%20I%20thought%20how%20can%20such%20a%20person%20be%20Prime%20Minister%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20clip%20from%20the%20interview%20aired%20on%20YouTube%20portal%20The%20Ewer%20(Chill-Pill)%2C%20does%20not%20fully%20capture%20the%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Aiyar%20was%20responding%20to%20whether%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20was%20capable%20enough%20to%20lead%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20make%20decisions.%20In%20his%20response%2C%20Mr%20Aiyar%20went%20back%20to%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20how%20she%20was%20once%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bgungi%20gudiya%26quot%3B%20(a%20mute%20doll)%20before%20she%20evolved%20into%20a%20formidable%20political%20force.%20Moving%20to%20her%20son%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20Mr%20Aiyar%20spoke%20about%20his%20academic%20failures%20and%20the%20initial%20surprise%20when%20he%20was%20chosen%20for%20the%20top%20post.%20Mr%20Aiyar%20then%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20now%20say%20he%20was%20an%20excellent%20Prime%20Minister.%26quot%3B%20The%20Gandhi%20family%20loyalist%20then%20referred%20to%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20widow%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20said%20she%20was%20tagged%20a%20foreigner%20when%20she%20started%20her%20political%20journey%20and%20later%20became%20a%20key%20player%20in%20the%20Indian%20political%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20said%20he%20did%20not%20know%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20functioned%20and%20took%20decisions.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20know%20their%20family%20history.%20That%20tells%20me%20they%20may%20seem%20incapable%20initially%2C%20but%20a%20change%20comes%20when%20they%20face%20challenges%20and%20show%20their%20capability.%20So%20we%20will%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20short%20clip%2C%20however%2C%20shares%20only%20Mr%20Aiyar's%20remark%20on%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20academic%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20clip%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Amit%20Malviya%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRajiv%20Gandhi%20struggled%20academically%2C%20even%20failing%20at%20Cambridge%2C%20where%20passing%20is%20relatively%20easy.%20He%20then%20moved%20to%20Imperial%20College%20London%20but%20failed%20there%20as%20well...%20Many%20questioned%20how%20someone%20with%20his%20academic%20record%20could%20become%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Let%20the%20veil%20be%20stripped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20were%20approached%20for%20their%20response%20to%20the%20well-circulated%20clip%2C%20they%20launched%20personal%20attacks%20on%20Mr%20Aiyar%2C%20who%20has%20often%20left%20the%20party%20red-faced%20with%20his%20off-the-cuff%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20veteran%20Harish%20Rawat%20called%20Mr%20Aiyar%20a%20%26quot%3Bfrustrated%20individual%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20gave%20the%20country%20a%20modern%20outlook.%20%26quot%3BHe%20took%20concrete%20steps%20for%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20the%20economy%20as%20well.%20Unfortunately%2C%20a%20section%20of%20the%20party%20(Congress)%20did%20not%20stand%20with%20him%2C%20or%20else%20the%20country's%20history%20would%20have%20been%20something%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Rawat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741248300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F0bk1in38_mani-shankar-aiyar-rahul-gandhi-ani-_625x300_15_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyar-asked-if-he-would-like-to-mentor-rahul-gandhi-his-reply-7860730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20veteran%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20pre-empted%20the%20row%20that%20his%20latest%20interview%20would%20spark%2C%20and%20said%20he%20was%20relieved%20that%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20had%20declared%20that%20his%20views%20don't%20represent%20the%20party%20position.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyar-asked-if-he-would-like-to-mentor-rahul-gandhi-his-reply-7860730%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Has%20Mayawati%20Given%20Up%20Completely%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20formidable%20figure%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20politics%2C%20Mayawati%2C%20today%20struggling%20to%20remain%20relevant%2C%20has%20accelerated%20the%20existential%20crisis%20facing%20her%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP).%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20at%20a%20party%20meeting%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20she%20expelled%20Akash%20Anand%2C%20her%20nephew%20and%20someone%20long%20seen%20as%20her%20political%20heir%2C%20from%20the%20BSP.%20Not%20only%20did%20she%20relieve%20Anand%20of%20all%20his%20responsibilities%2C%20but%20she%20also%20stated%20that%20she%20would%20never%20name%20anyone%20as%20her%20successor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fallout%20between%20Mayawati%20and%20Anand%20is%20not%20sudden.%20Last%20year%20in%20May%2C%20he%20was%20removed%20from%20all%20his%20posts%20due%20to%20some%20controversial%20remarks%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20though%20he%20was%20eventually%20reinstated%20a%20month%20later.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20trigger%20for%20Akash's%20expulsion%20seems%20to%20be%20his%20allegedly%20%E2%80%98arrogant'%20and%20%E2%80%98selfish'%20response%20to%20his%20suspension%20as%20national%20coordinator.%20Mayawati%20said%20he%20was%20acting%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20the%20influence%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20father-in-law%2C%20Ashok%20Siddharth%E2%80%94who%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20party%20last%20month%20for%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20split%20it%20down%20the%20middle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Slew%20Of%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20saga%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20BSP's%20decay.%20The%20inconsistent%20approach%20of%20%E2%80%98Behenji'%2C%20her%20absence%20from%20the%20electoral%20scene%2C%20the%20party's%20poor%20performance%20in%20elections%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20more%20popular%20Dalit%20youth%20icons%20like%20Chandrasekhar%20Azad%2C%20and%20the%20tag%20of%20being%20the%20%E2%80%98B-Team'%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20reduced%20the%20BSP%20to%20almost%20a%20non-entity%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20today.%20The%202027%20assembly%20elections%20might%20as%20well%20be%20the%20last%20nail%20in%20the%20party's%20coffin%20if%20Mayawati%20doesn't%20mend%20her%20ways%2C%20take%20some%20drastic%20steps%20to%20improve%20voter%20outreach%2C%20and%20revive%20its%20voter%20base.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20is%20almost%20on%20life%20support.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20last%20year%2C%20it%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat%2C%20with%20its%20vote%20share%20dropping%20to%20a%20dismal%202.3%25%2C%20compared%20to%203.7%25%20in%202019.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20garnered%20just%209.5%25%20votes%2C%20compared%20to%2019.4%25%20in%202019.%20In%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%20as%20well%2C%20the%20party%20won%20just%20a%20single%20seat%20with%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2013%25%2C%20over%209%20percentage%20points%20less%20than%20its%20tally%20in%202017.%20It%20has%20just%20one%20MP%20in%20Parliament%20today%2C%20that%20too%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20And%20given%20its%20strength%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly%2C%20even%20that%20MP%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20re-elected%20once%20he%20retires%20next%20year.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20Jatavs%E2%80%94the%20caste%20Mayawati%20belongs%20to%E2%80%94seem%20to%20have%20remained%20by%20her%20side.%20Even%20among%20Jatav%20Dalits%2C%20the%20support%20for%20her%2C%20according%20to%20CSDS%20data%2C%20slipped%20from%2087%25%20in%202017%20to%2065%25%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20election%2C%20to%2044%25%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Among%20non-Jatav%20Dalits%2C%20whom%20the%20BJP%20had%20anyway%20started%20wooing%20in%202014%2C%20the%20support%20for%20the%20BSP%20dropped%20from%2044%25%20to%2027%25%2C%20then%20to%2015%25%2C%20in%20the%20same%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'B-Team'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20opposition%20claims%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20Mayawati%20has%20done%20is%20due%20to%20the%20fear%20of%20ED%20or%20CBI%20action%20under%20the%20BJP's%20rule%20at%20the%20Centre.%20But%20this%20has%20cost%20Mayawati%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20its%20Muslim%20vote%20base%20and%20has%20earned%20it%20the%20tag%20of%20being%20the%20%E2%80%98B-Team'%20of%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BSP%20used%20to%20receive%20over%2020%25%20votes%20from%20Muslims%3B%20by%202024%2C%20this%20had%20fallen%20to%20just%205%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Chandrasekhar%20Azad's%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20(ASP)%20and%20his%20victory%20in%20Nagina%20is%20also%20symbolic%20of%20the%20BSP's%20decay.%20From%20this%20very%20district%E2%80%94Bijnor%E2%80%94had%20Mayawati%20made%20her%20electoral%20debut%20in%201989.%20Three%20decades%20later%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20last%20year%2C%20its%20candidate%20finished%20fourth%20in%20the%20Nagina%20seat%20with%20an%20embarrassing%201.3%25%20vote%20share.%20%C2%A0In%20fact%2C%20when%20Mayawati%20had%20placed%20her%20bets%20on%20Akash%20Anand%2C%20the%20latter%2C%20though%20not%20a%20candidate%2C%20delivered%20his%20debut%20electoral%20speech%20from%20Nagina%20as%20her%20heir%20apparent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpponents%20Are%20Closing%20In%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20elections%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20a%20do-or-die%20battle%20for%20Mayawati.%20The%20BSP%20will%20face%20a%20tough%20challenge%20from%20Chandrasekhar%20Azad%2C%20who%20is%20trying%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20the%20only%20Dalit%20champion%20in%20the%20state.%20Azad%20also%20belongs%20to%20the%20Jatav%20caste%20and%20is%20popular%20among%20young%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20with%20his%20%E2%80%98Pichda%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Minority'%20pitch%2C%20has%20already%20made%20a%20significant%20dent%20in%20the%20BSP's%20non-Jatav%20vote.%20According%20to%20CSDS%20data%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20bagged%2056%25%20non-Jatav%20support%20in%20last%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Naturally%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)-Congress%20alliance%20would%20hope%20to%20clinch%20the%20remaining%20Jatav%20too%20by%202027.%20The%20SP%2C%20which%20trailed%20behind%20the%20BJP%20by%209%25%20in%202022%2C%20needs%20to%20claim%20the%20BSP's%20support%20base%20in%20order%20before%20that%20to%20give%20a%20genuine%20fight%20to%20the%20BJP.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Regional%20Curse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20parties%20have%20a%20shelf%20life%20in%20India.%20Many%20are%20plagued%20by%20existential%20questions%20today%3A%20what%20becomes%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%3F%20Of%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20after%20Naveen%20Patnaik%3F%20Of%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20after%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%3F%20What%20does%20the%20future%20hold%20for%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20has%20now%20joined%20this%20unceremonious%20list%20too.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20does%20Mayawati%20have%20the%20hunger%20left%20to%20pull%20the%20BSP%20out%20of%20the%20throes%20of%20irrelevance%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741248300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fh0ec696_mayawati-pti_625x300_21_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhas-mayawati-given-up-completely-7860717%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20a%20formidable%20figure%20in%20Uttar%20Pradeshs%20politics%2C%20Mayawati%2C%20today%20struggling%20to%20remain%20relevant%2C%20has%20accelerated%20the%20existential%20crisis%20facing%20her%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhas-mayawati-given-up-completely-7860717%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTubers%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%2C%20Apoorva%20Makhija%20Questioned%20By%20Women's%20Panel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYouTubers%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20and%20Apoorva%20Mukhija%20reached%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20(NCW)%20questioning%20today%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20controversy%20that%20erupted%20over%20remarks%20made%20on%20the%20show%20India's%20Got%20Latent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women's%20panel%20had%20initially%20summoned%20Mr%20Allahbadia%2C%20Ms%20Makhija%2C%20Samay%20Raina%2C%20Apoorva%20Mukhija%2C%20Jaspreet%20Singh%2C%20Ashish%20Chanchlani%2C%20Tushar%20Poojari%2C%20Saurabh%20Bothra%2C%20and%20Balraj%20Ghai%20to%20appear%20last%20month.%C2%A0%C2%A0However%2C%20all%20the%20content%20creators%20failed%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20panel%2C%20citing%20concerns%20over%20personal%20safety%2C%20pre-scheduled%20travel%20commitments%2C%20and%20logistical%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanveer%20Allahbadia%20had%20sought%20a%20three-week%20extension%2C%20citing%20death%20threats%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20not%20attending%20the%20initial%20hearing.%20The%20panel%20granted%20his%20request%20and%20scheduled%20a%20new%20hearing%20date%20for%20March%206.%20Ms%20Mukhija%20had%20also%20raised%20safety%20concerns%20and%20requested%20to%20appear%20virtually%2C%20but%20the%20NCW%20denied%20her%20request%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20attend%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20after%20YouTuber%20and%20podcaster%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%2C%20known%20as%20BeerBiceps%2C%20made%20offensive%20remarks%20about%20parents%20and%20sex%20on%20Samay%20Raina's%20show%20India's%20Got%20Latent.%20The%20comments%20triggered%20widespread%20outrage%2C%20leading%20to%20multiple%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20from%20the%20Mumbai%20and%20Assam%20police%20visited%20Allahbadia's%20residence%20to%20record%20his%20statement%2C%20but%20found%20it%20locked.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Mr%20Allahbadia%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20social%20media%20saying%20that%20he%20was%20cooperating%20with%20the%20authorities%20and%20would%20be%20available%20for%20questioning.%20He%20also%20mentioned%20receiving%20death%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741248060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F1ce086fo_ranveer-allahbadia-apoorva-makhija-_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoutubers-ranveer-allahbadia-apoorva-makhija-questioned-by-womens-panel-7860577%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22YouTubers%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20and%20Apoorva%20Mukhija%20reached%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20(NCW)%20today%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20controversy%20that%20erupted%20over%20remarks%20made%20on%20the%20show%20India's%20Got%20Latent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoutubers-ranveer-allahbadia-apoorva-makhija-questioned-by-womens-panel-7860577%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20on%20being%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%2C%20anxiety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741247930000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118755164%2Cimgsize-45024.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-opens-up-on-being-diagnosed-with-anxiety-and-adhd-my-body-was-heating-up-at-social-gatherings%2Farticleshow%2F118755205.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118755205.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlia%20Bhatt%2C%20reveals%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%20and%20anxiety%20after%20experiencing%20physical%20symptoms%20and%20focus%20issues.%20Finding%20the%20diagnosis%20provided%20reassurance%20and%20guidance.%20The%20actress%20is%20currently%20busy%20with%20her%20YRF%20spy%20universe%20movie%20and%20Sanjay%20Leela%20Bhansali's%20'Love%20And%20War'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-opens-up-on-being-diagnosed-with-anxiety-and-adhd-my-body-was-heating-up-at-social-gatherings%2Farticleshow%2F118755205.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gambhir%20Targeted%20By%20SA%20Media%20With%20'Hollow%20Victory'%20Jibe%3A%20%26quot%3BCringe-Worthy...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20chatter%20over%20the%20'hybrid'%20nature%20of%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20and%20whether%20that%20handed%20India%20%26quot%3Bunfair%20advantage%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20campaign.%20India%20played%20all%20of%20their%20matches%20in%20Dubai%20after%20they%20refused%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20due%20to%20political%20tensions.%20However%2C%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20sharp%20retort%20to%20the%20comments%20and%20even%20went%20on%20to%20call%20the%20critics%20%26quot%3Bperpetual%20cribbers%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20the%20South%20Africa%20media%20has%20taken%20aim%20at%20the%20former%20India%20opener%20and%20criticised%20his%20%26quot%3Bcringeworthy%20arrogance%26quot%3B%20while%20stating%20that%20even%20if%20India%20triumph%20in%20the%20final%2C%20the%20victory%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bhollow%26quot%3B%20for%20Gambhir%20and%20Co.%20In%20a%20report%20published%20by%C2%A0South%20African%20media%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iol.co.za%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Fopinion%2Findia-may-win-champions-trophy-but-gambhir-will-know-its-a-hollow-victory-3e860a38-f310-42d0-8172-7b2ba4395c35%5C%22%3Eiol.co.za%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gambhir%20was%20slammed%20for%20his%20comments%20on%20the%20topic%20and%20the%20report%20went%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3Bhis%20arrogance%20throughout%20this%20whole%20situation%20is%20cringe-worthy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20the%20ICC%20Academy%20and%20Dubai%20International%20Stadium%20is%20only%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20apart%20seems%20to%20be%20completely%20lost%20on%20the%20former%20India%20opener.%20But%20that's%20not%20what%20has%20my%20back%20up.%20Gambhir's%20arrogance%20throughout%20this%20whole%20situation%20is%20cringeworthy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20every%20likelihood%20that%20India%20will%20go%20on%20to%20win%20their%20second%20successive%20major%20ICC%20trophy%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%20on%20Sunday%20when%20they%20face%20New%20Zealand%2C%20who%20beat%20South%20Africa%20in%20Wednesday's%20semi-final.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20when%20Gambhir%20raises%20the%20trophy%20towards%20the%20Dubai%20night%20skyline%20in%20celebration%2C%20being%20the%20fierce%20competitor%20that%20he%20is%2C%20he%20will%20know%20de