0of%20the%20US%2C%20India%2C%20Australia%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20specific%20issue%20of%20tariffs%2C%20the%20minister%20noted%20that%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20is%20currently%20in%20Washington%20to%20discuss%20a%20bilateral%20trade%20pact%2C%20following%20discussions%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Trump%20at%20the%20White%20House%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20very%20open%20conversation%20about%20it%20(tariffs)%20and%20the%20result%20of%20that%20conversation%20was%20that%20we%20agreed%20on%20the%20need%20for%20a%20bilateral%20trade%20agreement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20exchange%20with%20Chatham%20House%20Director%20Bronwen%20Maddox%2C%20the%20EAM%20covered%20a%20broad%20spectrum%20of%20issues%20including%20his%20%26quot%3Bcautious%20optimism%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20India-UK%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%20(FTA)%20negotiations%20after%20his%20ministerial%20discussions%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20complicated%20process.%20So%2C%20given%20the%20complexity%2C%20it's%20natural%20that%20it%20would%20take%20time%E2%80%A6%20from%20my%20discussions%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20(Keir)%20Starmer%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20David%20Lammy%20and%20%5BBusiness%5D%20Secretary%20Jonathan%20Reynolds%2C%20I%20got%20a%20consistent%20message%20that%20the%20British%20side%20is%20also%20interested%20in%20moving%20forward.%20I%20had%20a%20few%20points%20to%20convey%20on%20behalf%20of%20my%20concerned%20colleagues%20as%20well.%20So%2C%20I'm%20cautiously%20optimistic%20and%20hope%20that%20it%20doesn't%20take%20that%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20role%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20BRICS%20grouping%20of%20nations%20and%20relations%20with%20China%20were%20among%20the%20other%20major%20foreign%20policy%20issues%20touched%20upon%20during%20the%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20one%20of%20the%20few%20countries%20who%20have%20been%20regularly%20talking%20to%20both%20Moscow%20and%20Kyiv%20at%20various%20levels%E2%80%A6%20Wherever%20there's%20been%20a%20sense%20that%20India%20can%20do%20something%2C%20we%20have%20always%20been%20open-minded%20about%20it.%20Our%20consistent%20position%20has%20been%20that%20they%20need%20to%20do%20direct%20negotiations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20China%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20noted%20some%20positive%20movement%20since%20October%202024%2C%20including%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Mount%20Kailash%20pilgrimage%20route%20in%20Tibet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20very%2C%20very%20unique%20relationship%20with%20China%20as%20the%20only%20two%20billion%20plus%20populated%20countries%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%A6%20we%20want%20a%20relationship%20where%20our%20interests%20are%20respected%2C%20sensitivities%20are%20recognised%20and%20works%20for%20both%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20an%20audience%20question%20on%20%26quot%3Bsolving%26quot%3B%20issues%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20minister%20stated%3A%20%26quot%3BRemoving%20Article%20370%20was%20step%20number%20one%2C%20restoring%20growth%20and%20economic%20activity%20and%20social%20justice%20in%20Kashmir%20was%20step%20number%20two%2C%20and%20holding%20elections%20with%20a%20very%20high%20turnout%20was%20step%20number%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20part%20we%20are%20waiting%20for%20is%20the%20return%20of%20the%20stolen%20part%20of%20Kashmir%20which%20is%20under%20illegal%20Pakistani%20occupation.%20When%20that%20is%20done%2C%20I%20assure%20you%20Kashmir%20will%20be%20solved.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20is%20scheduled%20for%20talks%20with%20his%20Irish%20counterpart%2C%20Simon%20Harris%2C%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20